summary: I wanted a character that looked like she could handle herself in a fight, but at the same time pretty to look at
descriptionHtml:
I wanted a character that looked like she could handle herself in a fight, but at the same time pretty to look at. personally I like the result ;) my boyfriend and friends thought I should share her with the world, so here she is!

[b]she is level 1 and inside Helgen keep[/b]

if you want to change her appearance type showracemenu in the console, but when you do that her eye makeup disappears, under the Eyes category set tint and eyeliner all the way to the right (no eye shadow).

mods used:

Better females by Bella v3
No more blocky faces (install after better females)
CBBE (slim)
Covereyes 1

I\'m unsure about her hair, if it requires any mods, I have Hair Pack and ApachiiSkyHair installed but I think she uses standard hair. if she turns out to be bald, you know what to download!

the armor in the screenshots is Ancient Nord Armor and Saviors Hide CBBE v3

leave a comment if shes not turning out to be like in the screenshots, and I can try to help :)
author: jannicke93
